38325608e20e04cc17a7","tid":237323,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:16:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>點解你份人咁撚低劣？</strong></span></span><br />\n中蟈人DNA唔講得笑<br />\n我考完試日撚日搵你呀嫐主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba7e6b86be68a65f84229c1dd8202c94d07382f","tid":237323,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>支那仔被人撚狗撚到 1001 POST</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/219567/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/219567/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解入十連 post?<br />\n巴閉囉 爆 post 主義 推 post<br />\n我唔妥你 可以斷你<br />\n我唔鐘意你 可以恥笑你<br />\n𡃁仔你啤咩呀 出黎十連吖<br />\n十連呀<br />\n連我吖 連吖<br />\n我連你 你連我 點呀<br />\n你見過鯨大校舍未，你見過米八男神未呀<br />\n你話嫐巴係你偶像吖嘛 你見過嫐巴未<br />\n十連 post 揸 fit 人吖嘛 好巴閉呀 ?<br />\n你知唔知佢個 post 俾人騎劫掹唔到<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住佢癲咗，佢醫唔到<br />\n你知唔知嫐巴諗緊咩呀?<br />\n話俾你聽佢唔想做揸fit人<br />\n佢唔想開十連 post<br />\n但係佢無辦法 無得返轉頭<br />\n係呀 每個人都有偶像 我都有<br />\n其實 十唔十連 我理唔到咁多<br />\n但係我想話俾你聽 開錯 post 無得返轉頭㗎[/b]"},{"pid":"8fa737a34fbfcb1dc95bab237c29204d63e22c54","tid":237323,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>條賤種拎強姦慘劇黎講笑<br />\n聲稱要合法化強姦十點後外出嘅女人</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺網上唔代表可以乜都講<br />\n你上得連登就代表你係一個人<br />\n唔該你地似返個人<br />\n<br />\n認撚住條雞蟲份人係幾撚低劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eab649c69ea7e54c9896fe723a7ca45f195ae16","tid":237323,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"