2:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5156991fd92a26f105d118434ac783ae99e7b4e3","tid":237323,"uid":17189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T21:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>條賤種拎強姦慘劇黎講笑<br />\n聲稱要合法化強姦十點後外出嘅女人</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺網上唔代表可以乜都講<br />\n你上得連登就代表你係一個人<br />\n唔該你地似返個人<br />\n<br />\n認撚住條雞蟲份人係幾撚低劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢條雞蟲梗係想合法化啦<br />\n連雞都唔Show哩條死大陸哩無得叫<br />\n佢咪想強姦人免費1Q囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打我見你又好撚憎條契弟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇過你點樣狙擊佢再睇哩條大陸哩點臭串法所以咪咁撚憎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4f91a7f2c0a9b74638537293a73fc9b03a6fe7","tid":237323,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T21:48:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾狗你老母俾狗屌"},{"pid":"9f462f32e7498d88795deec547b8fe65873194f8","tid":237323,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddec9c7d3e5854d0c40c994d209f2f35e9b8e935","tid":237323,"uid":110846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主係大陸狗黎(已自認)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg&h=4ed886d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係樓主之前個名-連尼住(大佬)</span></strong></span><br />\n讀垃圾OU HD，打字用拼音。<br />\n之後俾巴打圍屌，死不悔改之餘，<br />\n仲笑鳩人讀書少，唔抵得人識打拼音！<br />\n堅稱自己係土生土長嘅香港人喎~~<br />\n<br />\n就算識打字嗰陣都要轉channel去諗嗰個字嘅蝗語點讀，再打出嚟。<br />\n點都慢過用倉頡速成就咁諗點打好撚多<br />\n除非佢本身就係蝗語channel，又或者講慣蝗語<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg&h=ca5c499d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本係大陸仔打啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唸又窩又奔，都唔知佢打乜柒！<br />\n你全家奔緊落地獄呀支那狗！！！！！<br />\n下世咪撚再落黎香港，生生世世做中蟈人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過追擊之下，終於承認自己係支那狗，<br />\n並聲稱自己永遠都唔上LIHKG<br />\n又改名-你仲唔仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/15/233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F15%2F233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg&h=443b5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好景不常，經過一個月潛水又俾我見返佢！<br />\n所以只好繼續我嘅追擊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條柒頭份人極度陰險，之前開post叫雞俾人放飛機開post起人底！<br />\n<br />\n小心呢件ptgf<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n仲話叫ptgf唔係叫雞喎，你咪撚玩啦！<br />\n人地唔撚so你好出奇咩？<br />\n雞都嫌棄你賤種畜生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多先，希望樓主真係好好守承諾，<br />\n唔好再上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bd14e069d8091bd7b0bb7ec3a7c7a99b679cf1e7","tid":237323,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1accc79c9fe4ffc74625a3f162f72c6c3a71cdfe","tid":237323,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"陸偉雄大律師指出，任何人在網上作出言行都不可違法，發放姦劫案受害者身分背景的人，隨時會干犯「妨礙司法公正」罪，即使他或她並無此動機，但亦會窒礙事主作證，及使其他人不敢舉報，警方會因應有關行為令事主受損失，可引用「不誠實使用電腦」罪名，檢控涉事網民，網民應克制。"},{"pid":"4ced6363b6d89964c1ecf4cfbe506dc8439e1685","tid":237323,"uid":17189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陸偉雄大律師指出，任何人在網上作出言行都不可違法，發放姦劫案受害者身分背景的人，隨時會干犯「妨礙司法公正」罪，即使他或她並無此動機，但亦會窒礙事主作證，及使其他人不敢舉報，警方會因應有關行為令事主受損失，可引用「不誠實使用電腦」罪名，檢控涉事網民，網民應克制。</blockquote><br />\n巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a1bc54293b6360e1705a18c583a59a0c988501","tid":237323,"uid":36480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:11:12.000Z","msg":"推一推 比人入黎block柒佢"},{"pid":"15fe4bbeb1515ed1876fed13e31cba5ed023bba5","tid":237323,"uid":41238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/10/175628_e863456a41625e2a6cb719d4debaf5e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2F175628_e863456a41625e2a6cb719d4debaf5e0.jpg&h=2c573a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應合法化強姦十點